item.dc:creator: @Cheesehunk Cheesehunk
item.description:
@Cheesehunk wrote:

Check your help thread, I showed you how to fix the Login.

Also, you could add random paths by doing something like this:

[hr]
[php]Procedure WalkToFlax1;
begin
//Walking proc’s here.
end;

Procedure WalkToFlax2;
begin
//Walking proc’s here.
end;

Procedure WalkToFlax3;
begin
//Walking proc’s here.
end;

Procedure WalkToFlax;
begin
case Random(3) of
0: WalkToFlax1;
1: WalkToFlax2;
2: WalkToFlax3;
end;
end;

begin
WalkToFlax;
PickFlax;
end;
[/php]
[hr]

Hope that helps.

P.S. Good job on the script.
